item.description:
Join Boston Rotaract in our 3rd annual speed dating night! All funds raised from this fun event will go towards the Dakar children’s health clinic and orphanage in Senegal. Come alone or bring a date and join us in raising funds to purchase infant necessities, medicines and vitamins. $15 per person - Every $ goes towards the Dakar Pouponnière **Only ages 21–30 please. 

For any questions, please don’t hesitate to contact Kaitlyn at internationalservice@bostonrotaract.org 

For more information about the Dakar Pouponnière visit their website: http://dakarpouponniere.com/en/index.htm
